# Services

User Registration and Authentication:

✅registerUser(userData)
✅authenticateUser(credentials)
✅generateOTP(userId)
✅sendOTP(userId, phoneNumber, otp)
✅verifyOTP(userId, enteredOTP)

User Profile Management:

✅getUserById(userId)
✅updateUser(userId, userData)
✅changePassword(userId, newPassword)
✅getReferrer(userId)
✅getReferredUsers(userId)
✅checkCreditRating(userId)
✅checkLoanEligibility(userId)
✅getLoanLimit(userId)

E-Wallet Management:

✅createWallet(userId)
✅linkBankAccountToWallet(walletId, bankAccountId)
✅linkUserToWallet(walletId, userId)
✅getWallet(userId)
✅performWalletTransaction(userId,customerWalletId,transactionData)
✅deleteWallet(userId)
✅remittanceToAgentWallet(loanId, agentWalletId, interestAmount)
✅transferWalletBalanceToBankAccount(agentWalletId, bankAccountId)
✅automateTransferToBankAccount(customerWalletId, bankAccountId, amount)

Bank Account Management:
✅createBankAccount(userId)
✅linkBankAccount(userId, bankAccountData)
✅verifyBankAccount(userId, bankAccountId)

Referral Code Management:

✅checkReferralEligibility(userId)
✅generateReferralCode(userId)
✅redeemReferralCode(userId, referralCode)
✅getReferralCodeByUserId(userId)

Loan Processing:

✅checkLoanEligibility(userId)
✅applyForLoan(userId, loanData)
✅calculateInterest(loanId)
✅calculateLoanRepaymentAmount(loanId)
✅approveLoan(loanId)
✅disburseLoan(loanId)
✅getLoanRepaymentStatus(loanId)
✅repayLoan(loanId, repaymentAmount)
✅generatePaymentLink(loanId, amount)
✅markLoanAsRepaid(loanId)
✅getUnpaidLoansByReferralCode(referralCode)

Notification Management:

✅sendNotification(userId, message)
✅notifyLoanApprovalToCustomer(userId)
✅notifyLoanRepaymentToCustomer(userId)
✅notifyLoanStatusToAgent(agentId, loanStatus)
✅sendSMSNotification(userId, message)

Transaction History:

✅createTransaction(userId,TransactionData)
✅getUserTransactions(userId)
✅getTransactionDetials(TransactionId)

User Verification:
✅verifyUser(userId, verificationData)
✅verifyAgentBankAccount(agentId)
✅acceptTermsAndConditions(agentId)

Support Card Management:

✅createSupportCard(userId, cardData)
✅updateSupportCard(userId, cardId, cardData)
